name: Scomp Link Access (V)
Lore: 'A computer connection access port used mainly by droids to plug into database networks and locate information, evaluate threats, execute diagnostics or perform maintenance.',
Text: 'USED: Take a non-[Episode I] droid (except IL-19) into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR Place a card from hand on Used Pile.STARTING: Deploy from Reserve Deck two always [Immune to Alter] Effects. If you have only one location (with less than 3 [Light Side Force]) (except Massassi Throne Room) on table, may deploy a [Cloud City] site. Place this Interrupt in hand.(Original Concept by Mike Tomashweski - PC Volunteer Award 2006)',
